These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-1::.
Flower: lily, tulip, orchid, daffodil, marigold, rose, balloon-flower
Sport: badminton, baseball, biathlon, cycling, parkour, skiing, volleyball
 1. Flower:lily is between Flower:daffodil and Flower:balloon-flower##2
 2. Flower:tulip is in the middle##1
 3. Sport:parkour is on the right of Sport:volleyball##1
 4. Flower:marigold is between Sport:biathlon and Sport:parkour##2
 5. Sport:baseball is on the right of Sport:skiing##1
 6. Sport:baseball is on the right of Flower:daffodil##1
 7. Sport:badminton is between Sport:cycling and Sport:biathlon##2
 8. Sport:baseball is on the left of Flower:balloon-flower##1
 9. Flower:marigold is on the left of Flower:rose##1
10. Flower:marigold is on the right of Sport:biathlon##1
11. Flower:rose is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Flower   | daffodil | lily | balloon-flower | tulip    | orchid | marigold   | rose    |
| Sport         | skiing  | baseball   | cycling | badminton | biathlon   | volleyball | parkour |

